steps.name: * Prepration
And I close all client application windows
* Create the document
Given I open hyperlink "e1cib/list/Document.AdditionalExpenses"
Then "Additional Expenses" window is opened
And I click the button named "FormCreate"
Then "Additional Expenses (create)" window is opened
* Fill the attributes
And I click Choice button of the field named "Company"
Then "Vendors" window is opened
And I go to line in "List" table
And I select current line in "List" table
And I move to the tab named "AdditionalExpensesSection"
* Method
And I select "By quantity" exact value from the drop-down list named "Variant"
* Fill the Items tabular part
And in the table "AdditionalExpenses" I click the button named "AdditionalExpensesSelectItems"
Then "Purchase Invoices" window is opened
And I go to line in "List" table
